        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/information-disclosure",
          "message": {
            "text": "Tool results from External API calls may contain sensitive data (user records, financial data, PII) that the Tool Server logs verbatim to the Audit Logger. If Audit Logger access is not restricted, this data becomes accessible to any process that reads the audit trail, including the Learning Loop's training pipeline.",
            "markdown": "Implement structured logging with field-level classification: PII and sensitive tool result fields MUST be hashed or tokenized before writing to the Audit Logger. The Tool Server MUST apply a log-before-hash policy (hash the content, log the hash) rather than logging raw sensitive content."
          },
          "level": "warning",
          "locations": [
