            "markdown": "Log every JSON-RPC tool invocation to the Audit Logger before execution: the calling agent's identity (verified from the caller token), the tool name, all parameters (hashed for PII), and the resulting output (hashed). Log entries MUST be written atomically before tool execution begins."
